# 🔐 Environment Variables Template
# Copy to .env and fill in your actual values
# NEVER commit .env to git - it's in .gitignore

# JWT Configuration (REQUIRED for real API integration)
# Get this secret from your team lead or Azure Key Vault
Authentication__AspNetIdentity__Jwt__SecretKey="your-real-jwt-secret-from-team-or-keyvault"
Authentication__AspNetIdentity__Jwt__Issuer="https://localhost:7297"
Authentication__AspNetIdentity__Jwt__Audience="FabrikamApi"

# Database Connection (OPTIONAL - only if using SQL Server)
ConnectionStrings__DefaultConnection="Server=fabrikam-dev-sql.database.windows.net;Database=fabrikam-dev-db;User Id=fabrikam-admin;Password=YOUR_SQL_PASSWORD_HERE;Encrypt=true;"

# Azure Key Vault (OPTIONAL - for advanced scenarios)
AzureKeyVault__VaultUrl="https://fabrikam-dev-kv-4651.vault.azure.net/"

# ====================================================================
# 📋 SETUP INSTRUCTIONS:
# ====================================================================
#
# 🚀 QUICK START (Development Only):
#   - No setup needed! Just run the API
#   - Uses built-in development secret
#   - Perfect for local testing and demos
#
# 🔗 TEAM INTEGRATION (Real Secrets):
#   1. Copy this file to .env
#   2. Get real JWT secret from team/Azure Key Vault  
#   3. Replace "your-real-jwt-secret..." with actual secret
#   4. Now your local API works with deployed services!
#
# 🔐 SECURITY LEVELS:
#   - Development: Built-in secret (safe for source control)
#   - Team .env: Real secret (never commit to git)
#   - Production: Azure Key Vault (managed security)
#
# 📚 More Info: docs/development/JWT-SECURITY-STRATEGY.md
